-- Russia May Ease Citizenship Rules for Those Born in Soviet Union
-- B y   S t e p a n   K r a v c h e n k o
-- 2012-07-09T10:56:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-09/russia-may-ease-citizenship-rules-for-those-born-in-soviet-union.html
Russia may ease citizenship
requirements for people born in the Soviet Union and their
direct descendants, as well as those whose families were
subjects of the tsarist empire, President  Vladimir Putin  said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stepan Kravchenko in Moscow at 
